ScreenLifeCycle
public class PastOutcomeRecordsScreen extends SinglePaginationTableScreen<AppointmentOutcomeRecord>
The PastOutcomeRecordScreen class displays a list of past appointment outcome for the patient. The class retreives the currently logged-in patient from LoginManager to access and display their data. The class extends SinglePaginationTableScreen to show these records in a paginated format.

This screen allows patient to view the detials of their past appointments, including the outcome of each consultation.
